'''天主教胡志明市總教區'''（{{vie|hn=總教分城庯胡志明|qn=Tổng giáo phận Thành phố Hồ Chí Minh}}；{{lang-la|Archidioecesis Hochiminhopolitanus}}）是[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]在[[越南|越南]]設立的3個天主教總教區之一。

2004年，有602,476名教友，佔轄區總人口11%，有195個堂區、519名司鐸、1,607名修士、3,382名修女。主教座堂設於[[西貢王公聖母教堂|西貢王公聖母教堂]]。現任總主教為{{link-en|阮能|Joseph Nguyễn Năng}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 19.10.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/19/191019a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019132848/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/10/19/191019a.html |archivedate=2019-10-19 |language=en |date=2019-10-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，輔理主教為{{link-vi|阮英俊|Louis Nguyễn Anh Tuấn}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Rinunce e nomine, 25.08.2017 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/08/25/0534/01186.html |publisher=Sala Stampa della Santa Sede |accessdate=2019-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019140314/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/it/bollettino/pubblico/2017/08/25/0534/01186.html |archivedate=2019-10-19 |language=it |date=2017-08-25 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，榮休總主教為[[范明敏|范明敏]][[樞機|樞機]]<ref>{{cite web |title=PHAM MINH MÂN Card. Jean-Baptiste |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_pham-minh-man_jb.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-10-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191019135727/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/documentation/cardinali_biografie/cardinali_bio_pham-minh-man_jb.html |archivedate=2019-10-19 |language=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==歷史==
1844年3月2日成立教區，1960年11月24日昇為西貢總教區，[[越南|越南]]統一以後，1976年11月23日，西貢總教區改名為胡志明市總教區。

